// ============================================================================
// BENEFITS FOR STREAM DECK DEVICES
// ============================================================================
//
// вң… No key names needed - only positions
// вң… Visual mapping matches physical grid exactly
// вң… Easy to understand: [row, col] = button position
// вң… Works with ANY grid size (2x2, 3x3, 4x4, 5x3, etc.)
// вң… Device-agnostic: Change device, same script structure
